1. *Majkl* je bio najbolji učenik u razredu. (Michael was the best student in the class.)
2. Ona je mislila da će *Majkla* nikad neće pronaći. (She thought she would never find Michael.)
3. *Majkla* je poštovan od svih u njegovoj porodici. (Michael is respected by everyone in his family.)
4. Ona je bila veoma srećna kada je pronašla *Majkla*. (She was very happy when she found Michael.)
5. *Majklova* brata je bila veoma ponosna na njega. (Michael's brother was very proud of him.)
6. Njihov otac je bio veoma zadovoljan *Majklovim* uspesima. (Their father was very pleased with Michael's successes.)